        "Description": "The client, who is a global transportation company wants to stop a global weapons trading syndicate which has been known to cause internal conflicts around the world. Our client has found that many members of Krondstat have been selling weapons to Kowoon which has then been passed on to rebellions within governments, in an attempt to stir global trade. Our client has asked that you eliminate the targets in the accidents requested due to them not wanting it to be traced back to them at all.",
